{"word":"Chains","slug":"chains","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Chains</b> Used as ornaments:<br/> - Worn by princes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=42'>Gen 41:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=7'>Dan 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=29'>Dan 5:29</a> <br/> - Worn on ankles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=50'>Num 31:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=19'>Isa 3:19</a> <br/> - Worn on the breastplate of the high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=14'>Exo 28:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=15'>Exo 39:15</a> <br/> - As ornaments on camels<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=26'>Jdg 8:26</a> <br/> - A partition of, in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=21'>1Ki 6:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=17'>1Ki 7:17</a> <br/> Used to confine prisoners<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=6'>Psa 68:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=149&verse=8'>Psa 149:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=4'>Jer 40:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=7'>Act 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=33'>Act 21:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=20'>Act 28:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=16'>2Ti 1:16</a><br/><a href='S:Fetters'>Fetters</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73&verse=6'>Psa 73:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=1&verse=9'>Pro 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=3&verse=7'>Lam 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=7&verse=27'>Eze 7:27</a>; <a href='B:'></a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=4'>2Pe 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=20&verse=1'>Rev 20:1</a>"}]}